{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_13_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 凄く心強いわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.5593206175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なら……私が今回は優を助ける\n優が生徒会長になれるように、私も手伝うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Then… I’ll help you this time.\nI’ll support you so you can become president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5593206175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4392749786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？\nで、でも瑠依ちゃんはうちが生徒会長になるんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!?\nB-but Rui-chan‚ me becoming president is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4392749786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8392749786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、正直に言えば、あまり納得はしていないわ\nトリエルの――三人の時間が減るのは、嫌だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ to be honest‚ I’m not entirely convinced.\nI don’t like the idea of our time as the three of us in TRINITYAiLE decreasing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これまで優は私がやりたいことを、支えてくれた\n私も……そしてすみれも、優に助けられてきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But up until now‚ you’ve supported everything I wanted to do.\nBoth I… and Sumire‚ have been helped by you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4482091903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "だから今度は、優のことを手伝いたいし、支えたいの\n今回は、私が優の助けになるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this time‚ I want to help and support you.\nThis time‚ I’ll be the one helping you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5274837493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……うち、絶対生徒会長になってみせる\nアイドル活動もちゃんとやります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan… I’ll definitely become president.\nAnd I’ll keep up my idol activities properly too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1608170826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.0608170826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、そうね……実は……まだちょっと、気持ちは……\n応援しきれていないんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… alright… actually… I still feel a little…\nlike I can’t fully support you yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "漫画に影響を受けたからって、運命だなんて……\nもし生徒会長になって、アイドル活動が疎かになったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just because you were influenced by a manga‚ calling it fate…\nIf you become president and your idol work suffers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1677333195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、ダメよ瑠依！\n私は優を手伝う、支えるって決めたんだもの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that’s not right‚ Rui!\nI’ve decided to help and support Yu!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2531534899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.4238334019
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6207356434
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、何やら複雑そうやなぁ……\nあんな、瑠依ちゃん、聞いて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ you look pretty conflicted…\nHey‚ Rui-chan‚ listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6207356434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちが生徒会長を目指すのは\n『ここまま』もきっかけの一つではあるんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I’m aiming to be student council president is…\n“Kokomama” is one of the reasons‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1238334019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7571667353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "この学校を、もっと良くしたいって想いはあるんよ\n……まだちゃんと、考えはまとまってへんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really want to make this school a better place.\n…I haven’t fully sorted my thoughts yet‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8238334019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.5238334019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのね……なら、いつかその考えがまとまったら\n私にも教えて。私ももう迷わない。全力で応援するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… then when you’ve sorted it out someday‚\ntell me. I won’t hesitate anymore—I’ll support you with everything I’ve got.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1653732806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9156699497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、瑠依ちゃんが応援してくれるなら\nこの選挙、なおさら負けられへんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. If you’re supporting me‚ Rui-chan‚\nthere’s no way I can lose this election!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5823366164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.9490032831
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、生徒会長選挙、必ず勝ちにいきましょう！\n一年生生徒会長、鈴村優を目指して！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ let’s make sure we win the student council election!\nAiming for first-year president‚ Yu Suzumura!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8880293527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、ほんまにええ子やわぁ\nしっかりしてるし、頼りになるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan is really such a good girl.\nShe’s reliable and really dependable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4380293527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "「ライブの準備は私に任せて、選挙頑張ってね！」\nなんて言われたら、より一層気合いも入るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Leave the live preparations to me and focus on the election!”\nWhen she says that‚ it fires me up even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7046960193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、私達、すみれに助けられることも多いわね\nでも……無理しないかちょっと心配だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we’re helped by Sumire quite often too.\nBut… I’m a bit worried she might be pushing herself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そうやね、そこはうちらも気を付けとこか\nすみれちゃんは頑張り過ぎるとこ、あるしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we should keep an eye on that too.\nShe does have a tendency to overdo it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1294810611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "なら、私が気を付けておくわ\n優は心置きなく選挙に集中してちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I’ll keep an eye on her.\nYou should focus on the election without worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんも、ほんまにありがとう\nうち、凄く心強いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ thank you so much too.\nI feel really reassured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3046059924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ところでな、実は今悩んでることがあって……\nちょっと相談に乗ってほしいんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ there’s something I’ve been struggling with…\nI’d like your advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9046059924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "……うち、生徒会長選の公約に迷っててな\nここ何日か、学校でいろんな人に質問したんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m having trouble deciding on my campaign promises.\nFor the past few days‚ I’ve been asking people around school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0379393258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.587940343
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.587940343
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.537940343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらこの学校が、もっと良くなると思います？\nなんでも聞かせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think would make this school better?\nPlease tell me anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.537940343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.8712736764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "学食のメニューにもっとボリュームがほしい……\nふむふむ、逆にハーフサイズも選べたらええかもなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“We want bigger portions in the cafeteria…”\nI see‚ maybe offering half-size options would be good too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.0841879359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.021291987
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.021291987
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.7712909697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "図書館にもっと漫画がほしい……\nそれはうちも思ってました！　置いてほしいなぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“We want more manga in the library…”\nI’ve thought that too! I’d love to have them there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.7712909697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.6212848662
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.6212848662
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 219.9712909697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "視聴覚室で映画が観たい？　分かるわ～！\nうちもあの大画面で映画やアニメ、観たいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to watch movies in the AV room? I get that!\nI’d love to watch movies and anime on that big screen too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.9712909697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 225.5879444121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "と、こんな感じで……図書室を漫画喫茶にするんと\n視聴覚室に座席を入れてミニシアターにするんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So yeah… turning the library into a manga cafe‚\nadding seating to the AV room to make it a mini theater‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.4379576364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "それと、学食のメニューを全て\n大盛とハーフサイズが選べるようにしたいんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and making all cafeteria menu items\navailable in large or half sizes… that’s kind of what I have in mind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.4046365101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "漫画喫茶とかミニシアターとか……\nそこまでいったらもう学校じゃないでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A manga cafe and a mini theater…\nAt that point‚ it’s not even a school anymore!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.3333455404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "せやろか？\n学校って、勉強やコミュニケーションのための場やろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?\nSchool is a place for studying and communication‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.0220618565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "好きな物で溢れとったら、もっと交流もしやすくなって\n感性も刺激されて、素敵な場所にならへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s filled with things people love‚ it’ll make interacting easier‚\nand stimulate creativity—wouldn’t that make it a great place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.3410461001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "それに、学食のメニューをある程度改革するなら\n『グミのトッピング』を選べるようにも出来るで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if we’re revamping the cafeteria menu‚\nwe could even add “gummy toppings” as an option.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.5553951899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "学食にグミ……それはちょっと、いいかも……\n味も選べるように……って、や、やっぱりダメよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gummy toppings in the cafeteria… that might actually be nice…\nBeing able to choose flavors too…—n-no‚ that’s not good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.3000223797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、好きな物を大事にする姿勢は素敵よ\nでも、勉学の場に遊びを持ち込み過ぎるのは良くないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that valuing what you love is wonderful.\nBut bringing too much play into a place of learning isn’t good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.9000223797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "ライブだってそうでしょ？　みんながライブ中に\nゲームをしたり漫画を読んでたら、もうライブじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the same with a live show‚ right? If everyone during a live\nwere playing games or reading manga‚ it wouldn’t be a live anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.5666890463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ、ほんまや……！　確かにそうかもしれへん\nうち、間違ってた。相談してみて良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you’re right…! That might be true.\nI was wrong. I’m glad I asked you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.8836942036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんの話を聞いて、他の生徒さんの意見も\nええ感じにまとまりそうやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing you out‚ and combining other students’ opinions‚\nI think I can put everything together nicely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.4503608703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……じゃあ、具体的に明日から\n選挙に向けて準備を進めていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good… then starting tomorrow‚\nlet’s begin preparing for the election in earnest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.333355713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "まずは早起きして、校門であいさつ運動やな\n顔と名前を覚えてもらわんとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ I’ll get up early and greet people at the school gate.\nI need them to remember my face and name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.9477079708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "それは……もう十分出来ている気がするけど\nそうね、明日から本格的に、頑張っていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think… you’ve already done that quite well.\nStill‚ from tomorrow‚ let’s give it our all for real.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.833355713,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}